BeerCalc - The program used to manage the supply of beer to the thirsty freshmans at DIKU.


Installation - Linux
====================

  1. Open a terminal.
  2. cd to and/or create the dir where you want the program to be located.
  3. Run: git clone git@github.com:RusKursusGruppen/beercalc.git ./
  4. You should now be ready to run the program.


Usage - Linux
=============

Just run: 

  sh linux.sh


